titleStmt.title: Des pendants de cleffs pour les femmes

zone.note: -upper body of mythical creature -Lower body of fish
Upper scroll motif with floral details

div.p: Joan Theodor de Br F. et excu des PENDANTs de Cleffs pour les Femmes, propre pour les Argentiers. etlicherleij, SCHLVESEL geheng, fur di weiber, zeher nutzlich fur di Goltschmiden und dere.
Made and published by Joan Theodor de Br Key bows for women, fit for silversmiths. Several key bows for women, very useful for Goldsmiths and others.
